Is the null graph triangle-free? Yes.
Is C_4 triangle-free? Yes.
Is K_4 triangle-free? No.
Is K_{3,5} triangle-free? Yes.
Is a tree triangle-free? Yes.
Is the M_4 Mycielski graph triangle-free? Yes.
Is Frucht graph triangle-free? No.
Is Coxeter graph triangle-free? Yes.
Is the (2,3) Kautz graph triangle-free when ignoring edge directions? No.
Is the Q_4 hypercube triangle-free? Yes.
